-- lib/constants.ttslua
-- Constants Library
-- Game constants, configuration values, and lookup tables for VTM5E module.
-- Shared constants and lookup tables for this VTM5E Tabletop Simulator module.
--
-- Agent guidance: .dev/HUDs & Overlays/Player HUD Overview.md (C.CHRONICLE_DATA.coteries/disciplines, phases); lib/json/PCS.json + lib/pcs_data.ttslua for PCs; .dev/EXTRACTABLE_FUNCTIONS_INDEX.md.

