-- #region Sites

-- Sites
-- Optional `isSilent = true`: full ambient mute (background, location ambience, weather); featured music may still be played via Storyteller action. Merge with `Soundscape.applyContext(Soundscape.contextFromSite(site))`.

-- NOTE for Asset Import Functionality:
-- Each `C.Sites` entry uses `localImage` (absolute `file:///...` or OS path to WEBP on disk) and `image` (Custom UI asset
-- name, e.g. siteCard_MySite) for XML `image=` attributes after cloud upload.
-- Generate manifest + Lua module from constants, then TTS upload + merge save URLs:
--   npm run custom-ui-assets:manifest-sites
--   npm run custom-ui-assets:pipeline -- --mode sites-from-constants --saveName <saveId>
-- Optional: `--skipMissing` on the pipeline or manifest script skips sites whose files are absent (partial batches).
-- Batched uploads (alphabetical C.Sites keys): `npm run custom-ui-assets:manifest-sites:batch` or `--batch` / `--batchMax` / `--batchStart` (see `.dev/custom-ui-assets/README.md`).
-- Folder-based workflow (no constants): `npm run custom-ui-assets:pipeline -- --mode directory --input <folder> --saveName <id>`.

